# Keep the build context small and deterministic.
# Everything here is excluded from `COPY . .`, so it never bloats the context,
# never busts the layer cache, and stale host build artifacts can't leak into
# the image (the build recompiles from source inside the SDK stage).

# .NET build outputs (rebuilt in-container)
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# IDE / editor
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo

# Source control & CI
.git/
.gitignore
.github/

# Docker files themselves
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

# Local secrets / env (never bake these into an image)
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/*.env
.env

# Test projects are not needed to publish the API
Tests/

# Misc
**/*.md
